Class LoggingInterceptor

java.lang.Object
  ch.iserver.ace.util.LoggingInterceptor
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.aopalliance.aop.Advice, org.aopalliance.intercept.Interceptor, org.aopalliance.intercept.MethodInterceptor
public class LoggingInterceptor
extends Object
implements org.aopalliance.intercept.MethodInterceptor

Interceptor that logs the method invocations to the given logger category. The log level used to log can be specified as constructor argument. It defaults to Level.INFO.
